WEBVTT

00:40.457 --> 00:43.418
ALL CHARACTERS, PLACES, GROUPS, AND
ORGANIZATIONS IN THIS WORK ARE FICTITIOUS

00:43.501 --> 00:46.379
SCENES WITH ANIMALS ARE STAGED
ACCORDING TO ANIMAL WELFARE GUIDELINES

01:25.877 --> 01:27.837
Do you know that it's because of you

01:27.921 --> 01:30.006
that our custodian just stopped cleaning?

01:32.342 --> 01:33.676
Have some coffee.

01:43.478 --> 01:46.272
It's for what happened in Seoul last time.

01:46.856 --> 01:47.774
Sure.

01:51.611 --> 01:52.821
Dae-bum.

01:54.155 --> 01:55.198
You know what?

01:55.865 --> 01:59.077
It won't be the worst thing
to grow old working here together, right?

02:00.120 --> 02:01.913
And we only have one guest. Bom.

02:01.996 --> 02:04.207
-And that lady.
-Right.

02:04.290 --> 02:07.127
Ms. Lee. That's only two guests.

02:07.210 --> 02:08.795
-And Jun.
-Gosh.

02:08.878 --> 02:10.338
Stop it.

02:10.922 --> 02:13.383
If you think about it,
not being able to work in Seoul

02:13.466 --> 02:14.926
isn't something to be sad about.

02:15.426 --> 02:17.262
The air is polluted there.

02:17.345 --> 02:20.515
And people are always stressed over work.

02:20.598 --> 02:22.600
Right. And the rent is expensive there.

02:22.684 --> 02:23.810
Exactly.

02:23.893 --> 02:26.354
The rent in Seoul is insane, right?

02:28.690 --> 02:31.234
When does the result come out?

02:32.235 --> 02:34.487
I don't know. Why do you ask?

02:35.238 --> 02:36.698
Don't look for me on that day.

02:37.949 --> 02:39.284
I'm going off the grid.

02:40.577 --> 02:44.539
You're going to have to promote this area
to the outsiders for us.

02:45.081 --> 02:48.001
You should do it
while we have a tenant there.

02:48.793 --> 02:51.796
I've already posted it online,

02:51.880 --> 02:53.214
so let's give it some time.

02:53.298 --> 02:55.216
Really? You already did that?

02:55.300 --> 02:56.718
Of course.

02:58.678 --> 02:59.679
Hello.

02:59.762 --> 03:01.973
-Goodness. Officer Kwak!
-Hello.

03:02.056 --> 03:03.892
-Have you been well?
-Of course.

03:03.975 --> 03:05.894
Here, Father. This is from Mother.

03:05.977 --> 03:07.437
-Gosh, what's this?
-Have a seat.

03:07.520 --> 03:09.522
-Have some coffee before you leave.
-Sorry.

03:09.606 --> 03:11.441
-I have somewhere to be.
-Really?

03:11.524 --> 03:13.526
-I'll come again next time.
-Mu-cheol.

03:14.152 --> 03:16.821
I was going to ask you a favor.

03:17.572 --> 03:18.823
What about?

03:18.907 --> 03:20.199
You know my building, right?

03:20.867 --> 03:21.951
Sure.

03:22.035 --> 03:25.204
Can you patrol around my building
every now and then?

03:25.788 --> 03:27.248
Did something happen?

03:27.832 --> 03:31.711
Some punk drew hideous graffiti
on my building last night.

03:33.171 --> 03:34.213
A graffiti?

03:34.797 --> 03:35.924
What did it say?

03:36.007 --> 03:39.969
It was something along the lines
of "I'm going to kill you."

03:40.053 --> 03:41.304
Goodness.

03:41.387 --> 03:43.306
We don't even have CCTV in that area.

03:43.806 --> 03:47.435
I apologize.
I'll be more vigilant from now on.

03:47.518 --> 03:50.188
Yes. Please keep an eye on it if you can.

03:50.772 --> 03:52.690
-Of course.
-I feel so relieved

03:52.774 --> 03:54.859
-thanks to you, Mu-cheol.
-Sure.

03:58.404 --> 04:00.490
Gosh, my head.

04:22.512 --> 04:23.638
I don't feel well.

04:29.519 --> 04:30.937
What's this?

04:34.649 --> 04:36.192
It's dried pollack soup.

04:57.463 --> 04:58.673
That's nice.

05:01.175 --> 05:04.387
Who did all this?

05:09.684 --> 05:12.270
Grandma wanted to thank you
for bringing Dad home.

05:12.895 --> 05:14.522
Also, thanks for the pencils.

05:15.148 --> 05:17.400
It's that student from the library.

05:33.082 --> 05:34.250
What is that?

05:42.633 --> 05:44.010
What happened to me?

05:46.471 --> 05:48.222
What did I do yesterday?

05:57.732 --> 06:00.443
WITHDREW: 400,000 WON
REMAINING BALANCE: 4.5 MILLION WON

06:00.526 --> 06:01.694
What? 400,000 won?

06:04.614 --> 06:06.324
When did I withdraw 400,000 won?

06:07.575 --> 06:09.327
What happened?

06:13.956 --> 06:16.542
WITHDREW: 500,000 WON
REMAINING BALANCE: 0 WON

06:17.710 --> 06:18.878
Zero?

06:26.469 --> 06:29.305
Ma'am, I came here yesterday, right?

06:30.515 --> 06:31.933
Are you finally sober?

06:32.975 --> 06:34.519
What's up with your face?

06:37.522 --> 06:40.233
I withdrew cash from here, didn't I?

06:41.859 --> 06:44.112
Don't you remember fighting the ATM?

06:46.280 --> 06:49.033
You! You took my money!

06:49.117 --> 06:50.284
Give it back!

06:50.368 --> 06:51.953
Give me back my money!

06:52.036 --> 06:53.788
Damn it. Give it back!

06:53.871 --> 06:56.165
-Gosh.
-Give me back my money!

06:56.249 --> 06:57.708
What's wrong with you?

06:57.792 --> 06:59.877
Why are you hitting this?
Is your hand okay?

06:59.961 --> 07:02.547
This thing ate up my money
and it won't give it back.

07:02.630 --> 07:05.174
I have so much more money than this.

07:06.843 --> 07:09.679
I was right to be worried
when you bought those liquor earlier.

07:09.762 --> 07:12.140
You can only withdraw up
to 400,000 won a day.

07:12.223 --> 07:13.516
You can't withdraw more.

07:13.599 --> 07:16.227
Why not? It's my money.

07:16.310 --> 07:17.687
Well…

07:18.980 --> 07:20.606
Come back again when you're sober.

07:20.690 --> 07:22.942
No. I have to withdraw the money now.

07:23.025 --> 07:25.528
-Immediately!
-Hey!

07:27.488 --> 07:28.614
Sober up.

07:29.198 --> 07:32.410
And go to the bank downtown tomorrow
to withdraw your money.

07:33.619 --> 07:37.123
Right. I can always go to the bank.

07:37.707 --> 07:38.791
Thank you so much.

07:43.087 --> 07:45.423
Gosh, your money. Hey!

07:46.007 --> 07:49.385
You're leaving breadcrumb trails
with money.

07:50.178 --> 07:52.513
You've got a rough night ahead of you.

07:52.597 --> 07:55.558
Why are you acting like this
in the middle of the night?

07:55.641 --> 07:57.435
-I'm so sorry.
-Goodness, gracious.

07:59.312 --> 08:02.815
You shouldn't be out this late
wandering around drunk.

08:02.899 --> 08:05.109
-How will you take care of the money?
-I'm sorry.

08:05.193 --> 08:07.028
Gosh. Put the money in here.

08:10.114 --> 08:12.200
Goodness. Here.

08:12.283 --> 08:13.451
-Now go.
-What?

08:14.118 --> 08:16.245
Why are you giving this to me?

08:19.999 --> 08:21.876
Here, you can use this.

08:23.336 --> 08:25.213
If you want to give me money,

08:26.088 --> 08:28.382
give it to me when you're sober tomorrow.

08:28.466 --> 08:31.677
Why won't you take it? I'm loaded!

08:31.761 --> 08:33.804
Just put your shoes back on and go home!

08:34.347 --> 08:37.391
-Go! Go home!
-No. I don't want to.

08:37.475 --> 08:38.601
Hurry up and go!

08:39.185 --> 08:41.437
-Bye, bye.
-Gosh.

08:41.521 --> 08:44.607
-Goodbye!
-Goodness.

08:45.399 --> 08:47.610
The liquor drank you last night.

08:49.654 --> 08:52.156
So I… and the money…

08:52.240 --> 08:54.033
And the plastic bag…

08:54.116 --> 08:56.536
I put it in a black plastic bag
in case you lose it.

08:59.121 --> 09:02.291
When I was walking by here again,

09:02.375 --> 09:04.835
was I carrying the black plastic bag?

09:04.919 --> 09:07.088
You didn't come back
until the store was closed,

09:07.171 --> 09:08.381
so I wouldn't know.

09:12.301 --> 09:13.636
Did you lose it?

09:15.513 --> 09:18.558
Hurry and visit the bank again.
You might've left it there.

09:20.768 --> 09:21.936
Thank you.

09:33.406 --> 09:35.950
Chang-su!

09:36.033 --> 09:37.326
Come out here for a moment.

09:39.620 --> 09:42.373
Goodness. What brings you here?

09:43.040 --> 09:45.876
There's a lot you're upset about
because of me, right?

09:46.586 --> 09:48.713
-Sorry?
-I understand.

09:48.796 --> 09:50.923
You must've been irritated

09:51.007 --> 09:52.842
about losing the building.

09:53.426 --> 09:55.845
-That's not true, sir.
-Is that why you did it?

09:56.470 --> 09:57.638
-Sorry?
-What did you say?

09:58.639 --> 10:00.099
What are you talking about?

10:00.600 --> 10:04.604
I'm asking if you guys did that
on my building last night.

10:04.687 --> 10:06.022
-What?
-What's this nonsense?

10:06.105 --> 10:07.315
On a witch-hunt again?

10:07.398 --> 10:09.525
Get lost. We have a business to run.

10:10.109 --> 10:13.195
You guys are busted.

10:14.030 --> 10:15.448
This here.

10:17.533 --> 10:20.661
Be honest with me here and
tell me what you did with this last night.

10:20.745 --> 10:21.871
Ridiculous.

10:22.663 --> 10:23.789
That canister?

10:23.873 --> 10:24.874
NO PARKING

10:24.957 --> 10:26.000
We wrote that.

10:26.584 --> 10:27.585
Why?

10:27.668 --> 10:29.962
Do we need your approval
to write that over there?

10:30.046 --> 10:33.049
Why are you trying to pick a fight
with ridiculous accusations?

10:33.132 --> 10:36.052
What did you say?
How dare you take that tone with me?

10:36.135 --> 10:37.720
Is it a fight you want?

10:37.803 --> 10:38.971
-All right then.
-Please.

10:39.055 --> 10:41.641
We'll both be
on the prime-time news today.

10:41.724 --> 10:43.726
-Please stop.
-Come over here!

10:43.809 --> 10:45.728
-Goodness, gracious.
-Calm down, please.

10:45.811 --> 10:47.063
-Come here.
-I apologize.

10:47.146 --> 10:48.356
A black plastic bag?

10:49.148 --> 10:50.858
Who would put their money in there?

10:50.941 --> 10:51.817
Why?

10:52.485 --> 10:54.862
-It wasn't here?
-If it was,

10:54.945 --> 10:56.530
someone must have taken it.

10:56.614 --> 10:58.240
It's money in a plastic bag.

11:00.034 --> 11:04.372
Would it be possible to check
the CCTV footage for the ATM?

11:05.539 --> 11:07.166
We have some procedures.

11:08.000 --> 11:10.378
So please fill this out
and come back tomorrow.

11:10.461 --> 11:12.880
-So the stamp…
-Is there any way I can see it today?

11:12.963 --> 11:14.757
This is really urgent.

11:14.840 --> 11:15.966
That won't be possible.

11:16.050 --> 11:17.134
Please fill this out

11:17.218 --> 11:18.719
-and come back tomorrow.
-Seong-man.

11:18.803 --> 11:21.931
-Isn't she the one you searched before?
-Please, I need it today.

11:22.014 --> 11:24.225
I'll go and watch it in a flash.

11:24.308 --> 11:26.560
Don't mind her.

11:26.644 --> 11:28.145
So what were we talking about?

11:28.229 --> 11:29.480
Seong-man.

11:29.563 --> 11:32.483
Loans are different
from lending money to a friend.

11:32.566 --> 11:34.068
-Next in line, please.
-Hold on. What's going on there?

11:34.151 --> 11:36.028
Hey, how about just 20 million won?

11:36.112 --> 11:38.072
-Next in line.
-Please.

11:38.155 --> 11:41.158
-Please, I'm begging you.
-What's wrong?

11:41.867 --> 11:44.537
Hello. We met the other time.

11:45.871 --> 11:47.123
Hello.

11:48.749 --> 11:51.752
Do you know what time you were here
approximately?

11:52.795 --> 11:54.547
What time was it?

11:55.131 --> 11:57.675
Why ask for the footage
if you don't even know the time?

11:57.758 --> 11:59.385
It's fine. We can just look for it.

12:03.055 --> 12:05.933
Here. Isn't this you?

12:06.851 --> 12:08.519
This is you, right?

12:08.602 --> 12:11.355
-Goodness.
-I think that is me.

12:11.439 --> 12:13.441
Why are you crawling in?

12:13.524 --> 12:15.776
You seem… What was wrong with you?

12:15.860 --> 12:18.696
Hey, she was drunk.

12:19.363 --> 12:20.865
Goodness.

12:20.948 --> 12:25.244
Why did you come in drunk
looking to withdraw money?

12:26.203 --> 12:27.121
What's that?

12:27.204 --> 12:29.039
Oh, my goodness. Look at you.

12:29.707 --> 12:32.710
Are you talking about
that black plastic bag?

12:32.793 --> 12:34.462
This must be it.

12:34.545 --> 12:37.756
You're holding it like a purse.
I thought it was a purse.

12:38.632 --> 12:40.009
You're struggling.

12:40.092 --> 12:42.553
I don't think you…

12:42.636 --> 12:47.016
It seems like you couldn't
remember your PIN code.

12:47.516 --> 12:48.642
I'm sorry.

12:49.518 --> 12:51.896
-He's right.
-Gosh, that startled me.

12:53.522 --> 12:54.690
I don't think you withdrew…

12:54.773 --> 12:56.525
Where did you go?

12:57.026 --> 12:58.777
Oh, you fell. That surprised me.

12:58.861 --> 13:00.738
Gosh, this is annoying. Just skip over.

13:02.364 --> 13:03.741
Goodness.

13:05.117 --> 13:07.536
-Did you get the money or…
-She must have withdrawn it.

13:07.620 --> 13:08.704
Stop here.

13:11.624 --> 13:13.584
-There you go.
-You got the money.

13:13.667 --> 13:16.128
Why would you withdraw
so much money late at night?

13:16.212 --> 13:17.588
Goodness.

13:17.671 --> 13:19.798
You should have put it in your wallet.

13:19.882 --> 13:21.717
Why would you put it in a plastic bag?

13:21.800 --> 13:23.344
You didn't leave the money.

13:24.553 --> 13:27.890
You're supposed to pull the door,
not climb on it.

13:28.474 --> 13:30.226
Gosh, this is annoying. Fast forward.

13:30.309 --> 13:33.395
And you just left like that.

13:34.688 --> 13:36.357
Thank you for showing me this.

13:36.440 --> 13:39.318
I think you dropped it on your way back.
You should look for it.

13:39.401 --> 13:40.653
-Okay?
-Okay.

13:41.987 --> 13:43.447
Hold on!

13:43.531 --> 13:44.907
-Who is this?
-What's this?

13:44.990 --> 13:46.909
-Something flew by.
-Play it.

13:48.452 --> 13:49.662
-What?
-What?

13:50.454 --> 13:52.623
-Something flew by.
-Is that me?

13:53.332 --> 13:55.292
-Who else would it be?
-You tripped again.

13:55.376 --> 13:56.544
Someone came running.

13:59.588 --> 14:01.757
That long-haired guy is Dae-bum.

14:04.301 --> 14:06.345
Why would he be here at that hour?

14:06.887 --> 14:08.305
This punk.

14:08.389 --> 14:11.016
He picked up the money, but not you.

14:13.394 --> 14:14.478
Look at her.

14:14.979 --> 14:17.773
Look how relaxed she is
now that her exam is over.

14:17.856 --> 14:18.899
I wasn't sleeping.

14:18.983 --> 14:21.193
-Hello, Yeo-reum.
-Hello.

14:22.444 --> 14:26.365
Mr. Librarian, could we talk for a moment?

14:26.448 --> 14:27.575
Sure, of course.

14:30.494 --> 14:32.746
Where are you two going?

14:33.789 --> 14:34.957
Go back to sleep.

14:35.708 --> 14:38.294
-Where are you going?
-Go to sleep.

14:38.377 --> 14:40.504
Why are you leaving me all alone?

14:41.088 --> 14:43.299
Did we…

14:43.883 --> 14:45.759
We met yesterday, right?

14:46.468 --> 14:47.344
Yes.

14:48.345 --> 14:50.347
Let's talk over some cold drinks.

14:51.181 --> 14:52.308
Thank you.

14:52.391 --> 14:55.269
She doesn't remember seeing you yesterday.

14:56.103 --> 14:57.313
Really?

14:59.189 --> 15:00.482
By any chance,

15:00.566 --> 15:03.694
do you remember the black plastic bag…

15:04.528 --> 15:06.739
that I was carrying?

15:07.323 --> 15:08.449
Of course.

15:08.532 --> 15:11.702
We watched the CCTV footage from the bank,

15:11.785 --> 15:14.038
and you took
the black plastic bag with you.

15:15.164 --> 15:16.290
I was…

15:17.166 --> 15:19.335
carrying it for you
so you wouldn't lose it.

15:19.877 --> 15:21.003
What about that?

15:21.086 --> 15:26.467
Could you tell me
what happened then in detail?

15:26.550 --> 15:29.345
She's been freaking out
because she lost that plastic bag.

15:29.428 --> 15:30.387
What?

15:30.471 --> 15:31.805
Please tell me.

15:36.060 --> 15:37.186
Last night,

15:38.145 --> 15:40.481
you tripped in front of the bank.

15:41.482 --> 15:43.359
-What's with her?
-Gosh.

15:43.859 --> 15:45.486
My money.

15:46.070 --> 15:47.112
Are you okay?

15:49.823 --> 15:51.283
Mr. Librarian.

15:54.411 --> 15:57.247
How did you come to find me
from so far away?

15:57.331 --> 15:59.708
I'll carry this in case you lose it.

15:59.792 --> 16:00.876
I'll give it back.

16:01.794 --> 16:03.921
I'm a bit drunk.

16:05.464 --> 16:08.425
-I'm a little bit drunk.
-Right.

16:09.009 --> 16:10.177
Are you okay?

16:10.260 --> 16:13.222
Goodness.

16:16.558 --> 16:19.728
I've seen this happen before somewhere.

16:19.812 --> 16:20.729
Sorry?

16:21.230 --> 16:23.023
Where was it?

16:24.733 --> 16:25.859
The library!

16:25.943 --> 16:27.277
Yes! The library!

16:27.820 --> 16:31.740
Why do you always show up
whenever I'm drunk?

16:32.324 --> 16:34.076
-When did I…
-Ready.

16:35.619 --> 16:36.787
-Sorry?
-Ready?

16:37.413 --> 16:40.791
Ready! Why do you appear before my eyes

16:41.375 --> 16:44.878
Whenever I'm drunk

16:44.962 --> 16:46.630
-Everyone!
-Come on, let's go.

16:46.714 --> 16:49.425
Why do you appear before my eyes

16:50.009 --> 16:53.345
Whenever I'm drunk

16:53.429 --> 16:55.848
Blah blah blah

16:55.931 --> 16:59.309
Why does your face keep
Appearing in my mind

17:05.107 --> 17:07.359
You're going home now, right?

17:07.443 --> 17:09.528
-Home?
-Yes.

17:11.238 --> 17:12.573
The billiard club?

17:12.656 --> 17:13.741
Yes.

17:15.367 --> 17:16.869
That's not a home.

17:23.834 --> 17:25.127
Gosh, that hurts.

17:25.210 --> 17:28.338
Nothing happened on the way home, right?

17:29.757 --> 17:31.050
In the morning,

17:31.967 --> 17:33.177
my face…

17:34.511 --> 17:36.930
You guys didn't
have a fight yesterday, right?

17:43.729 --> 17:44.938
Mr. Librarian.

17:45.522 --> 17:47.733
What brings you all the way here?

17:48.442 --> 17:49.943
You didn't take this with you.

17:54.239 --> 17:58.077
There's something
I've always wanted to ask you.

17:58.160 --> 17:59.161
Okay.

18:00.454 --> 18:02.873
-Is it okay if I ask right now?
-Sure.

18:10.547 --> 18:14.009
On the day
we slept in the library together…

18:15.886 --> 18:16.720
Sorry?

18:18.263 --> 18:19.348
What?

18:19.431 --> 18:21.809
Do you seriously not remember that day?

18:21.892 --> 18:22.935
That's not what I mean.

18:23.018 --> 18:25.813
We slept together
in the library that night.

18:25.896 --> 18:27.439
We didn't sleep together.

18:27.523 --> 18:29.399
-We slept in different rooms.
-Forget it.

18:30.359 --> 18:32.194
That's not the issue here.

18:33.946 --> 18:37.282
In the morning, did you hear me or not?

18:39.409 --> 18:41.328
What was I supposed to hear?

18:44.623 --> 18:48.127
The trickle.

18:50.003 --> 18:52.172
I do not understand
what you're talking about.

18:55.092 --> 18:56.426
Stop acting like you didn't.

19:03.809 --> 19:05.269
That really hurt.

19:05.853 --> 19:08.272
Why did you just do that to me?

19:08.355 --> 19:10.774
Why do you keep pushing me?

19:10.858 --> 19:12.401
You almost tripped, so…

19:12.484 --> 19:15.279
You've been pushing since a while ago.

19:15.362 --> 19:18.323
You didn't even use your hand,
but you used that plastic bag!

19:18.407 --> 19:19.533
Am I that filthy?

19:20.534 --> 19:22.286
Am I possessed or something?

19:22.369 --> 19:25.080
Look at this. You're avoiding me again.

19:25.164 --> 19:26.915
Please.

19:26.999 --> 19:29.793
All I want to do is live my life.

19:29.877 --> 19:32.921
All I want to do is live my life
drunk like this.

19:33.005 --> 19:36.550
So please just leave me alone!

19:37.843 --> 19:39.428
I'm so upset.

19:39.511 --> 19:42.764
Indeed. I'm also wondering
what I'm doing here right now.

19:42.848 --> 19:45.726
Please. I beg of you.

19:46.393 --> 19:48.937
It's nice to meet all of you.

20:03.702 --> 20:05.037
That hurts.

20:06.788 --> 20:08.540
Is my nose gone? I think it's gone.

20:08.624 --> 20:10.209
No, your nose is still intact.

20:11.543 --> 20:12.669
My nose.

20:12.753 --> 20:14.087
But there's a scar.

20:17.341 --> 20:20.093
You just dodged, didn't you?

20:22.346 --> 20:24.890
-I'm sorry.
-So it's true.

20:26.350 --> 20:29.353
So it's true that everyone hates me here.

20:29.436 --> 20:30.520
Well, you were…

20:31.730 --> 20:32.940
It's fine.

20:33.023 --> 20:34.858
Today is the last day.

20:36.735 --> 20:39.154
Hold this. Grab this.

20:46.328 --> 20:47.913
So how old are you?

20:48.497 --> 20:50.540
I'm 28 years old.

20:50.624 --> 20:51.625
For real?

20:53.335 --> 20:57.130
We're the same age!
Hey, we're the same age.

20:57.214 --> 20:59.258
Hey, follow me. I'll buy you something.

21:00.509 --> 21:01.927
Hey, come with me.

21:02.010 --> 21:03.303
Hurry up.

21:10.852 --> 21:13.230
We're here. Finally here!

21:13.772 --> 21:15.899
We're here! It's this place.

21:15.983 --> 21:18.860
Hey, buy everything you want to eat.
It's on me.

21:19.486 --> 21:21.113
I don't think we can right now.

21:22.030 --> 21:23.115
Why not?

21:23.198 --> 21:24.950
The store is closed.

21:25.033 --> 21:26.994
ANGOK SUPERMARKET

21:30.664 --> 21:34.376
We have some liquor left in my house.

21:34.459 --> 21:36.962
-Let's go!
-I'll be going home from here.

21:37.045 --> 21:38.463
What?

21:39.047 --> 21:40.382
No!

21:41.341 --> 21:43.468
I can't take that. No!

21:52.561 --> 21:53.478
Hey!

21:53.979 --> 21:56.315
I told you to take this with you!

21:57.399 --> 22:01.403
You threw me that bag and just left?

22:01.486 --> 22:02.529
Yes.

22:04.740 --> 22:05.824
This means

22:06.992 --> 22:09.953
that you dropped the bag somewhere
on your way home.

22:12.497 --> 22:14.583
I am sorry.

22:15.292 --> 22:17.919
I should have taken you
back to your home safely.

22:18.003 --> 22:19.004
No, it's fine.

22:20.881 --> 22:24.634
Anyway, thank you for last night.

22:29.973 --> 22:30.974
I told you so.

22:31.058 --> 22:34.186
I told you nothing good will happen
if you live there.

22:36.354 --> 22:37.773
Yeo-reum, goodbye.

22:38.482 --> 22:39.691
That looks painful.

22:42.819 --> 22:44.863
What happened? Tell me.

22:44.946 --> 22:46.239
-You want to know?
-Yes.

22:46.323 --> 22:47.866
Goodness.

22:53.955 --> 22:56.792
If I wasn't there,
she couldn't have watched the footage.

22:56.875 --> 22:59.628
I begged Yeong-sam to let her watch it.

23:01.630 --> 23:05.258
Weren't you tired from driving that night?
But you still went out?

23:05.342 --> 23:07.636
I was only out for a walk.

23:08.428 --> 23:10.472
Dae-bum sure is young.

23:11.056 --> 23:14.226
Why do people act like that
when they're drunk?

23:14.309 --> 23:16.019
Tell me about it.

23:16.103 --> 23:18.396
Drinking always gets the best of us.

23:18.480 --> 23:21.108
She lost all her money,
so she'll be drinking again today.

23:21.191 --> 23:23.026
The way I see it,
she'll never find that money.

23:23.110 --> 23:25.195
She lost all her money? How much?

23:26.822 --> 23:28.782
-Fifty million won?
-"Fifty million."

23:28.865 --> 23:30.742
Not that much. She lost five million.

23:30.826 --> 23:31.910
Five million.

23:31.993 --> 23:34.412
Then she should call the cops.

23:35.247 --> 23:37.707
You think that'll help her find the money?

23:37.791 --> 23:39.793
Even if I don't try to kick her out,

23:39.876 --> 23:41.795
she can't afford to live here anymore.

23:41.878 --> 23:44.548
Ji-yeong, I'm heading out.

23:44.631 --> 23:45.549
Where?

23:45.632 --> 23:48.218
-I might run late.
-Where are you going?

23:50.887 --> 23:51.972
He's acting weird.

23:52.556 --> 23:53.932
What's so weird?

23:54.015 --> 23:55.934
Why are you always making a fuss here?
Get out of here.

23:56.017 --> 23:56.977
Me?

23:57.727 --> 23:59.729
"Master yourself, master the enemy."

23:59.813 --> 24:02.482
If you know yourself and your enemy,
you'll never lose.

24:02.566 --> 24:05.026
I don't know what you're fighting,
but I hope you win.

24:05.110 --> 24:06.027
Good luck.

24:06.611 --> 24:09.197
Hey, Ji-yeong. When do you get off work?

24:09.906 --> 24:12.117
-In two days.
-Goodness.

24:20.667 --> 24:22.043
Where are you?

24:24.045 --> 24:25.380
Let's see.

24:25.964 --> 24:28.258
Why did I withdraw money when I was drunk?

24:29.384 --> 24:31.761
Hey, did you not see where I put the bag?

24:31.845 --> 24:34.014
Remember, Yeo-reum.

24:35.265 --> 24:36.349
Darn it.

24:41.771 --> 24:42.939
Please.

24:43.732 --> 24:45.984
Please be it.

24:47.027 --> 24:49.905
Please, I beg you.

24:53.950 --> 24:55.660
Damn it!

25:03.126 --> 25:04.252
GRANDMA WANTED TO THANK YOU
FOR BRINGING DAD HOME

25:04.336 --> 25:05.253
ALSO, THANKS FOR THE PENCILS

25:13.178 --> 25:14.387
Anyone home?

25:15.013 --> 25:16.139
Who is it?

25:22.771 --> 25:25.440
Oh, my. Hello.

25:25.982 --> 25:28.652
Goodness. What brings you here?

25:28.735 --> 25:30.070
Come on in.

25:30.153 --> 25:33.031
-Hello.
-The place is a bit of a mess.

25:35.659 --> 25:36.701
Sit here.

25:37.285 --> 25:39.537
-Thank you.
-I finally got to meet you again.

25:39.621 --> 25:41.706
I was curious how you were.

25:42.332 --> 25:43.708
-So?
-Well,

25:43.792 --> 25:46.336
I was wondering
where your granddaughter is.

25:46.920 --> 25:48.338
You didn't meet her?

25:48.421 --> 25:50.090
She went to your house this morning.

25:50.966 --> 25:52.050
No, I didn't.

25:52.634 --> 25:54.594
So you didn't.

25:57.681 --> 25:58.890
By the way,

25:59.516 --> 26:01.476
did you try the dried pollack soup?

26:02.060 --> 26:04.354
She randomly called me in the morning

26:04.437 --> 26:07.691
and asked me
how to make dried pollack soup.

26:10.527 --> 26:11.611
I see.

26:12.279 --> 26:13.947
It was delicious.

26:14.698 --> 26:16.491
I hope she cooked it well.

26:19.953 --> 26:24.040
When did the two of you become friends?

26:29.796 --> 26:32.215
-I'll be going now.
-All right.

26:33.550 --> 26:35.802
I picked some tomatoes recently.

26:35.885 --> 26:38.096
-Give me a second.
-It's fine, ma'am.

26:38.179 --> 26:39.681
Just wait here a bit.

26:40.598 --> 26:42.934
You really don't need to get it.
I'll get going.

26:50.442 --> 26:51.484
Wait.

26:52.319 --> 26:53.695
Here, take this.

26:57.115 --> 26:58.366
My granddaughter.

26:59.284 --> 27:00.869
Please take good care of her.

27:10.795 --> 27:15.258
Let's start here and search
everywhere I could have gone.

27:16.176 --> 27:19.179
I must find it.
I will find it no matter what.

27:26.061 --> 27:28.813
Could I look in your plastic bag?

27:34.903 --> 27:36.029
Gosh!

27:36.613 --> 27:38.656
-What are you doing?
-I lost something.

27:39.491 --> 27:40.617
Announcement to all residents.

27:40.700 --> 27:42.702
The lady that lives by the stream

27:42.786 --> 27:46.790
in the billiard club has lost her money.

27:46.873 --> 27:50.794
She says it was lost when she was wasted
from liquor last night.

27:50.877 --> 27:53.630
If any of the residents
find a black plastic bag

27:53.713 --> 27:58.259
holding 4.5 million won,

27:58.343 --> 28:02.263
Please report it to the community center.

28:03.056 --> 28:05.350
I repeat.

28:05.433 --> 28:10.230
If any of the residents find
a black plastic bag with 10,000 won bills,

28:10.313 --> 28:14.651
please notify the community center.

28:35.338 --> 28:36.339
Ms. Lee.

28:40.635 --> 28:41.678
Well…

28:42.679 --> 28:43.763
Here.

28:56.943 --> 28:58.611
Where did you find this?

28:59.237 --> 29:00.405
Last night,

29:01.489 --> 29:04.868
I took it home by accident.

29:06.703 --> 29:07.912
What?

29:08.538 --> 29:11.666
I thought that I gave it to you.

29:13.710 --> 29:16.254
You said you gave it to me before.

29:16.337 --> 29:17.797
That I took it.

29:18.423 --> 29:19.549
I'm sorry.

29:22.510 --> 29:23.845
You know

29:24.804 --> 29:26.598
I've been looking for this all day.

29:27.348 --> 29:28.558
Darn it.

29:28.641 --> 29:31.394
Did you just not care
since it's not your problem?

29:32.061 --> 29:33.188
I am sorry.

29:33.271 --> 29:36.900
I clearly asked you this afternoon.

29:37.400 --> 29:39.402
I remember asking you.

29:48.411 --> 29:49.537
Anyway,

29:51.539 --> 29:53.541
thank you for finding it.

30:19.651 --> 30:22.403
Grandma told me you came looking for me.

30:28.201 --> 30:29.828
Why were you looking for me?

30:36.042 --> 30:38.920
Nothing's wrong anymore.
The problem is solved now.

30:42.507 --> 30:44.259
So I can go, right?

30:46.845 --> 30:47.971
By the way…

30:50.932 --> 30:54.102
thank you for the dried pollack soup.

30:55.436 --> 30:56.479
Sure.

30:57.146 --> 30:59.065
But be careful.

30:59.148 --> 31:01.276
You can end up dead drinking like that.

31:05.071 --> 31:06.155
Do you…

31:08.992 --> 31:10.660
want some ramyeon?

31:11.703 --> 31:12.704
Sorry?

31:16.541 --> 31:19.210
I'm sorry,

31:19.294 --> 31:21.004
but can you wait just a minute?

31:21.087 --> 31:23.798
I think I need to go buy some ramyeon.

31:25.383 --> 31:27.010
Let's go together then.

31:28.094 --> 31:30.013
I don't want to stay alone
in someone else's home.

31:31.347 --> 31:32.348
Sure.

31:36.644 --> 31:37.854
Who is it?

31:41.316 --> 31:42.358
Excuse me!

31:50.491 --> 31:53.077
Hey, Heo Jae-hun! What are you up to?

31:53.161 --> 31:54.579
You knew it was me?

31:54.662 --> 31:58.708
Why would you wear a mask
when it's so obvious?

31:58.791 --> 32:00.126
Do you know him?

32:00.919 --> 32:03.588
No. You don't need to know him. Let's go.

32:03.671 --> 32:05.256
Wait. What do you mean?

32:05.840 --> 32:07.342
Hello.

32:07.425 --> 32:10.595
I'm Heo Jae-hun, Bom's classmate.

32:10.678 --> 32:13.681
But why were you in that building?

32:14.265 --> 32:15.725
Well,

32:15.808 --> 32:19.228
Bom doesn't come to school often
so I was worried,

32:19.312 --> 32:21.439
and I kind of missed her.

32:21.522 --> 32:23.942
Stop spewing nonsense.

32:24.025 --> 32:26.361
-Let's just go.
-Wait.

32:27.028 --> 32:28.488
Where are you two going?

32:28.571 --> 32:29.948
To buy ramyeon.

32:30.531 --> 32:31.783
Really? That's great.

32:31.866 --> 32:33.618
I make the best ramyeon.

32:33.701 --> 32:35.078
-If you…
-Don't follow us.

32:35.161 --> 32:37.080
Hey, let's go together.
I'm a master at it.

32:37.163 --> 32:39.165
-I said get lost.
-But you have to try.

32:40.667 --> 32:42.418
Let's go together.

32:44.796 --> 32:47.256
What happened to you?

32:50.009 --> 32:51.844
Were you looking for Yeo-reum's money?

32:51.928 --> 32:52.929
Yes.

32:53.763 --> 32:55.848
-Did you find it?
-Yes.

32:56.724 --> 32:57.892
Really?

32:57.976 --> 32:59.978
Impressive. I thought it was a lost cause.

33:01.437 --> 33:03.064
So you gave it to her?

33:04.607 --> 33:05.733
Yes.

33:08.611 --> 33:12.615
Don't you think you're meddling
too much in other's business?

33:12.699 --> 33:14.659
-This isn't like you.
-Ji-yeong.

33:16.786 --> 33:18.037
I'm hungry.

33:19.747 --> 33:21.874
This place is so cool, Yeo-reum.

33:21.958 --> 33:23.501
It's like a studio in New York.

33:24.377 --> 33:25.753
New York, my foot.

33:25.837 --> 33:28.423
I thought you were injured before.
Are you okay?

33:28.506 --> 33:30.383
I'm strong, so it's fine.

33:31.217 --> 33:32.593
Should I cook the ramyeon there?

33:33.469 --> 33:35.930
-I'll cook it.
-No, it's fine. I got it.

33:36.014 --> 33:39.350
You two don't even lift a finger.

33:39.434 --> 33:41.436
You'll be dazzled when you try my ramyeon.

33:41.519 --> 33:43.938
So, does the water boil
from you running your mouth?

33:44.022 --> 33:46.357
-Actually, fire does that.
-So annoying.

33:46.441 --> 33:48.192
I shouldn't have let you tag along.

33:55.783 --> 33:59.495
Is it okay if I call you Bom?

34:01.122 --> 34:02.290
Sure.

34:02.373 --> 34:04.917
I have something to tell you.

34:05.626 --> 34:07.045
What is it?

34:08.046 --> 34:09.172
Bom.

34:11.424 --> 34:12.592
I'm sorry.

34:13.342 --> 34:15.595
-I'm so sorry.
-What?

34:16.596 --> 34:18.806
All of a sudden? Why?

34:19.599 --> 34:21.350
About visiting your home

34:22.477 --> 34:24.020
and misunderstanding you.

34:25.396 --> 34:27.106
I'm sincerely sorry.

34:28.066 --> 34:30.318
Why are you apologizing?

34:31.069 --> 34:33.237
I was the one being mean.

34:33.321 --> 34:35.990
You had to pay a lot for the dog
because of me.

34:36.074 --> 34:37.200
That's fine.

34:38.034 --> 34:40.578
I'll pay you back as much as I can.

34:41.162 --> 34:44.540
Are you saying you're going to
get revenge on me?

34:45.541 --> 34:47.335
That's not what I mean.

34:48.503 --> 34:50.254
-Yeo-reum!
-Hey!

34:50.338 --> 34:52.006
What happened?

34:52.090 --> 34:53.966
I didn't do anything.

34:54.050 --> 34:55.176
This is…

34:56.135 --> 34:59.597
It's because there's a leak in the pipe,
and it's only taped up.

35:03.684 --> 35:06.395
-Hey, what are you doing?
-Move your hand.

35:07.730 --> 35:11.234
You're going to have to throw that away.
The pipe is shattered.

35:11.818 --> 35:12.777
Really?

35:12.860 --> 35:15.196
I'll go to Mr. Bae and get a new one.

35:15.279 --> 35:17.156
-Stay here.
-No need.

35:17.240 --> 35:19.075
We agreed that I'd fix these things.

35:19.158 --> 35:20.827
What? That's ridiculous.

35:20.910 --> 35:22.829
Just wait here. I'll get you a new one.

35:22.912 --> 35:24.747
-Let me tag along.
-Hey.

35:24.831 --> 35:27.917
Just stop getting in the way,
mop up the floor,

35:28.000 --> 35:30.086
and watch the dog properly.

35:30.169 --> 35:31.504
Hey!

35:31.587 --> 35:33.589
-I'll leave it to you, then.
-Yeo-reum!

35:40.221 --> 35:42.974
What's your name?

35:44.100 --> 35:45.268
Mr. Bae!

35:47.311 --> 35:48.437
Who is it?

35:49.063 --> 35:50.815
Gosh, you're here.

35:50.898 --> 35:53.109
Mr. Bae, how could you be like this?

35:53.693 --> 35:55.194
I know.

35:56.696 --> 35:58.865
-I'm sorry.
-You should be.

35:58.948 --> 36:01.909
The water pipe shattered
so she can't use the water there.

36:01.993 --> 36:03.536
The sink was breaking down.

36:04.120 --> 36:06.914
Shouldn't the landlord
be fixing it for the tenant?

36:11.252 --> 36:13.129
-You're talking about that?
-Then what?

36:13.212 --> 36:14.505
It's fine, Bom.

36:15.339 --> 36:16.757
I can fix it myself.

36:16.841 --> 36:19.427
-Just give me a pipe for the sink.
-No way.

36:20.303 --> 36:21.470
I'll fix it.

36:22.054 --> 36:24.223
I should be the one fixing it.

36:24.307 --> 36:27.393
You two can head home first.

36:27.476 --> 36:29.061
I'll be there with the parts.

36:29.145 --> 36:30.104
-Mr. Bae.
-Yes?

36:30.188 --> 36:32.773
You better hurry. We need to cook ramyeon.

36:32.857 --> 36:34.317
All right. I'll hurry.

36:34.400 --> 36:36.986
Yeo-reum, you should go with Bom.

36:37.820 --> 36:39.030
Let's go.

36:51.000 --> 36:52.084
Bom!

36:53.669 --> 36:54.962
Bom, come out here!

36:56.297 --> 36:59.175
-What do you want?
-Just come down here.

36:59.967 --> 37:01.552
Who are you? You come down too.

37:01.636 --> 37:02.511
Okay.

37:06.891 --> 37:10.019
You're so annoying. What do you want?

37:10.895 --> 37:12.563
Look who's here.

37:14.315 --> 37:16.192
You're the kid from the library.

37:16.275 --> 37:18.527
He's my son.

37:18.611 --> 37:20.905
Say hello to the grown-ups.

37:20.988 --> 37:21.948
Hello.

37:22.573 --> 37:23.532
Hey.

37:24.075 --> 37:26.619
He really wanted to see Billiard Lady.

37:26.702 --> 37:28.454
Me?

37:28.537 --> 37:30.248
What's up with you all of a sudden?

37:31.499 --> 37:34.335
Anyway, I brought some things you can use,

37:34.418 --> 37:36.003
so why don't we bring these up?

37:36.087 --> 37:38.256
Hello, I'm Bom's friend from school…

37:38.339 --> 37:41.008
Great. Good to see you.
You carry the heavy things with me.

37:41.092 --> 37:44.053
Bom and Yeo-reum.
You can just move the small things.

37:44.136 --> 37:46.013
And Jun. You know what to do.

37:46.097 --> 37:47.181
The lights.

37:48.516 --> 37:49.976
Are you giving those to me?

37:50.059 --> 37:52.061
They're nothing special.
Try carrying this.

37:52.144 --> 37:53.646
-It's light.
-Well…

37:53.729 --> 37:56.816
You're giving her
all of this for free, right?

37:56.899 --> 37:59.610
Of course it's for free.

37:59.694 --> 38:01.529
You're giving me all of these?

38:01.612 --> 38:04.240
-It's not much anyway.
-Let's just go up.

38:04.323 --> 38:06.242
-Go up.
-He's the generous type.

38:06.325 --> 38:07.952
That's not heavy. Come here.

38:08.035 --> 38:09.287
Get the big things first.

38:09.370 --> 38:11.122
Come over there. Grab this.

38:18.212 --> 38:20.798
Geun-ho. What are you doing over there?

38:20.881 --> 38:22.675
Come and eat.

38:39.525 --> 38:40.484
Geun-ho.

38:41.485 --> 38:45.448
You can never go outside, okay?

38:49.910 --> 38:52.371
Should we place it next to the bed?

38:54.206 --> 38:56.584
The lights are working well now.

38:56.667 --> 38:57.877
Thank you.

38:59.545 --> 39:02.340
Look at you. You're pretty good, Bom.

39:02.423 --> 39:06.177
I'm the only one who knows
how to do these things at home.

39:08.679 --> 39:10.806
Hey, Bom.

39:12.350 --> 39:15.686
About the part-time job I offered you,

39:15.770 --> 39:18.522
that's between us, okay?

39:19.815 --> 39:21.150
What's with you today?

39:21.776 --> 39:23.694
Does Yeo-reum have something on you?

39:24.779 --> 39:25.946
Like what?

39:27.740 --> 39:29.200
You didn't…

39:29.909 --> 39:31.327
Did you hear something?

39:32.703 --> 39:34.205
So there is something, then.

39:34.747 --> 39:35.998
What do you mean?

39:36.540 --> 39:38.167
Yeo-reum! It's working now.

39:39.377 --> 39:40.920
Did you fix it?

39:42.004 --> 39:44.590
-You can fix things like this?
-What a surprise, Bom.

39:45.549 --> 39:46.967
Tell me something you can't do.

39:47.551 --> 39:50.346
I knew it when I saw you
ripping off that tape.

39:50.429 --> 39:51.680
You're like Macgyver.

39:52.556 --> 39:55.017
Why does he keep talking?

39:55.601 --> 39:58.270
The door downstairs doesn't lock,
so I'll go take a look.

40:08.322 --> 40:11.242
-Excuse me. Here.
-It's fine.

40:11.867 --> 40:15.079
-You gave me so many--
-Hold it.

40:17.998 --> 40:20.459
There. It's sturdy now.

40:21.043 --> 40:21.877
Here.

40:22.628 --> 40:23.587
It's fine.

40:23.671 --> 40:26.966
I also brought you a lock chain.

40:27.049 --> 40:29.760
-You have to keep your doors locked.
-Okay.

40:29.844 --> 40:33.055
You saw the hideous graffiti.

40:33.931 --> 40:36.058
-Please take this.
-No need.

40:36.642 --> 40:39.103
Just think of it as an all-inclusive deal.

40:39.186 --> 40:42.022
-But still, it's too much.
-It's all right.

40:42.106 --> 40:44.191
They are all used products anyway.

40:44.275 --> 40:47.653
Just use them well and return them later.

40:48.696 --> 40:49.822
I almost forgot.

40:49.905 --> 40:51.073
Hey, Jun!

40:52.700 --> 40:54.452
He's bringing it.

41:00.332 --> 41:01.459
I'm sorry.

41:03.169 --> 41:04.295
About what?

41:07.798 --> 41:10.426
He broke open his piggy bank

41:10.509 --> 41:12.928
to buy this for you.

41:13.679 --> 41:17.224
Why are you being so nice to me today?

41:18.809 --> 41:20.144
Yeo-reum.

41:21.020 --> 41:23.772
What I'm about to say right now

41:24.857 --> 41:27.693
is a bit embarrassing for me.

41:28.819 --> 41:29.945
Well…

41:31.030 --> 41:32.031
Goodbye.

41:32.114 --> 41:35.784
My son loves to go to the supermarket
in the morning to buy pastries.

41:35.868 --> 41:39.288
And on his way out of the store today,

41:40.080 --> 41:42.791
he picked up the money. Your money.

41:45.586 --> 41:47.171
He's the one who found it?

41:47.254 --> 41:48.672
Tell me about it.

41:48.756 --> 41:51.300
Isn't it a relief
that my son picked it up though?

41:51.383 --> 41:53.135
Where did he find it?

41:54.428 --> 41:55.638
Well, actually…

41:56.931 --> 41:58.891
-Right here.
-Here?

42:04.605 --> 42:05.898
No way!

42:07.650 --> 42:11.570
He picked up a plastic bag
loaded with money on the street,

42:11.654 --> 42:15.783
thinking that this was
a gift for him from the heavens.

42:15.866 --> 42:18.953
He's read too many comic books.

42:19.036 --> 42:21.038
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

42:21.622 --> 42:22.748
But…

42:23.582 --> 42:25.584
Mr. Librarian had it.

42:25.668 --> 42:27.253
That was because

42:27.336 --> 42:30.714
my son heard the announcement
that my dad made,

42:30.798 --> 42:32.716
and that made him realize
what was going on.

42:32.800 --> 42:35.844
After hearing that, he got scared
and ran over to Dae-bum.

42:35.928 --> 42:37.721
And I went to the PC cafe with it…

42:37.805 --> 42:42.309
What's ridiculous is that he went
running to Dae-bum, not to me.

42:46.021 --> 42:47.273
I've been meaning to ask.

42:47.356 --> 42:50.651
Did Dae-bum mention my son

42:51.860 --> 42:53.696
when he gave you the money?

43:03.163 --> 43:04.456
No, he didn't.

43:07.334 --> 43:09.545
I wanted to ask you a favor.

43:09.628 --> 43:10.963
I don't want anyone

43:11.589 --> 43:14.258
to know about what Jun did.

43:14.341 --> 43:16.176
Of course. I won't tell anyone.

43:16.260 --> 43:18.596
Thank you so much.

43:20.347 --> 43:21.599
And I'm very sorry.

43:23.017 --> 43:24.393
I'll be going then.

43:25.185 --> 43:26.228
It's…

43:27.479 --> 43:29.106
It's not Jun's fault.

43:29.732 --> 43:32.109
After all, I'm the one who lost it.

43:32.693 --> 43:33.986
And don't worry.

43:34.069 --> 43:36.739
I'd be too embarrassed
to talk about what happened.

43:38.032 --> 43:39.450
Thank you so much.

43:41.410 --> 43:46.373
If there's anything you need
or something that needs to be fixed,

43:46.457 --> 43:48.500
call me immediately, okay?

43:49.877 --> 43:51.128
Thank you.

43:58.927 --> 44:01.055
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

44:04.850 --> 44:05.851
Hey, Yeo-reum.

44:05.934 --> 44:08.729
Look how much better it looks.
It finally feels like a home.

44:08.812 --> 44:10.272
Indeed.

44:10.356 --> 44:12.399
Mr. Bae finally did some good today.

44:13.067 --> 44:14.068
Is that pizza?

44:14.652 --> 44:16.153
-Yes.
-I've been craving this.

44:16.236 --> 44:17.488
I'm hungry. Can we eat it?

44:17.571 --> 44:19.323
Of course.

44:19.406 --> 44:22.868
Hey. Why are you still here
when you're not even cooking ramyeon?

44:22.951 --> 44:25.579
-Get lost.
-Stop being so stingy about food.

44:26.163 --> 44:28.040
By the way, what's the dog's name?

44:29.833 --> 44:31.043
He doesn't have one yet.

44:31.126 --> 44:33.921
Really? Then let's give him a name.

44:34.588 --> 44:37.716
Well, I actually have a name in mind.

44:37.800 --> 44:39.051
What is it?

44:39.134 --> 44:41.470
His fur is snow white,

44:41.553 --> 44:44.765
so how about Gyeo-ul, as in "winter"?

44:44.848 --> 44:46.475
Named after seasons, just like us.

44:47.142 --> 44:48.018
That's brilliant!

44:48.102 --> 44:49.436
-Really?
-Yes.

44:49.520 --> 44:51.730
What? That sounds weird.

44:51.814 --> 44:52.981
How about this?

44:53.065 --> 44:54.358
What about Demian?

44:54.441 --> 44:56.318
"Demian"? Demian, my foot.

44:56.402 --> 44:58.070
You just keep eating your pizza.

44:58.153 --> 44:59.738
Where's Demian?

44:59.822 --> 45:01.448
-You want pizza?
-Hey!

45:01.532 --> 45:02.658
-Don't give him pizza!
-You can't give him pizza!

45:02.741 --> 45:04.660
-Demian can't…
-You like the name, right?

45:05.536 --> 45:07.121
You called him Demian.

45:07.204 --> 45:09.039
-I did? When?
-You did.

45:09.123 --> 45:11.250
-I said Gyeo-ul.
-So it's decided, Demian.

45:11.333 --> 45:12.751
-I called it Gyeo-ul, right?
-She said Demian.

45:12.835 --> 45:14.086
I like Gyeo-ul better.

45:14.169 --> 45:15.838
You see? She likes Gyeo-ul better.

45:15.921 --> 45:19.800
PARKING LOT

45:22.302 --> 45:23.512
-Hey, Jun.
-Yes?

45:24.388 --> 45:26.557
-I'm heartbroken.
-Why?

45:26.640 --> 45:28.600
How could you tell Dae-bum first

45:28.684 --> 45:30.686
and not me?

45:31.478 --> 45:32.729
I'm very upset.

45:33.272 --> 45:34.648
Dad, what about that?

45:35.357 --> 45:36.692
You go bring it.

45:42.364 --> 45:43.615
What's this?

45:47.744 --> 45:49.371
Dad!

45:50.622 --> 45:52.458
-What?
-That.

45:54.710 --> 45:55.919
Open it.

45:56.003 --> 45:58.297
THANK YOU
FROM YEO-REUM

45:59.089 --> 46:01.300
Gosh, this lady.

46:03.427 --> 46:04.595
It's fine.

46:05.304 --> 46:08.974
The Billiard Lady gave it to us
to say thank you.

46:09.057 --> 46:11.518
-Really?
-Yes. You can have it.

46:14.062 --> 46:15.189
-Jun.
-Yes?

46:15.772 --> 46:18.400
You can't tell Grandpa
what happened today.

46:18.484 --> 46:19.485
Sure.

46:20.152 --> 46:23.489
Dad. I'm hungry. Can we also have pizza?

46:23.572 --> 46:25.115
Gosh, you brat.

46:25.657 --> 46:27.117
What kind of pizza do you want?

46:28.035 --> 46:29.286
-Bulgogi!
-Bulgogi!

46:29.369 --> 46:30.537
-Deal!
-Deal!

46:31.079 --> 46:33.415
-You order it. You have their number.
-Okay.

46:51.642 --> 46:52.893
I thought everyone in this town…

46:54.186 --> 46:58.899
No, I thought everyone in
this world hated me.

47:05.447 --> 47:07.699
I don't remember anything else,

47:07.783 --> 47:09.493
but I do remember this one thing.

47:11.495 --> 47:12.579
That is…

47:13.455 --> 47:14.706
hatred.

47:18.544 --> 47:20.754
I wanted to leave this place,

47:20.837 --> 47:22.965
so I wished all my money was gone.

47:26.385 --> 47:30.806
In my world, I was the victim.
And they were the assailant.

47:33.183 --> 47:36.061
But the opposite happened today.

47:39.481 --> 47:40.857
Where did you get those tomatoes?

47:41.775 --> 47:42.943
Your Grandma

47:43.777 --> 47:45.862
gave me these.

47:45.946 --> 47:46.989
Really?

47:47.698 --> 47:49.408
When did she give you these?

47:51.326 --> 47:52.202
Yeo-reum.

47:53.036 --> 47:59.376
Did you know this is where Dae-bum
used to live when he was young?

48:00.419 --> 48:01.461
No.

48:02.671 --> 48:06.508
To be exact, his family ran
the billiard club in this building.

48:09.386 --> 48:11.096
Then who is Seon-a?

48:11.179 --> 48:13.181
Seon-a is Dae-bum's older sister.

48:13.265 --> 48:15.851
Apparently, his older sister was
an absolute genius.

48:16.643 --> 48:19.062
SEON-A

49:03.482 --> 49:05.984
You must have heard about Jun.

49:06.777 --> 49:08.236
It was my fault for not telling you.

49:09.071 --> 49:12.240
More people die from loneliness
than starvation these days.

49:12.324 --> 49:13.992
You should go out and meet someone.

49:14.076 --> 49:15.577
Are you two married?

49:15.661 --> 49:17.621
No. We're not.

49:17.704 --> 49:21.375
He's too competent to be here
working for a countryside library.

49:21.458 --> 49:23.418
You must care about him a lot.

49:23.502 --> 49:25.754
We've spent a long time together.

49:25.837 --> 49:28.006
You're finally going to make it to Seoul.

49:28.090 --> 49:29.091
Come with me.

49:31.301 --> 49:34.388
Subtitle translation by: Jea-Heon Chung
